                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--doc-text);">Asynchronous & Streaming</h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-2" style="color: var(--doc-text-secondary);">
                        <li><code class="px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm" style="background: var(--doc-method-bg);">async_read_file</code> - Async file read</li>
                        <li><code class="px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm" style="background: var(--doc-method-bg);">async_write_file</code> - Async file write</li>
